item.title: Machine Learning Fireside Chats by BBC Blue Rooms
item.description: Yesterday I attended for the first time the Machine Learning Fireside Chats meetup run by the BBC Blue Room. Even though it was quite far from work and home I could not help going after seeing the name of the speakers on the line up.
